/www.theverge.com/2023/11/8/23953022/ humane-ai-pin-价格规格泄漏&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/8/23953022/humane-ai-pin-price-specs-leak" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/8/23953022/ humane-ai-pin-price-specs-leak</id><author><name>大卫·皮尔斯</name></author></entry></feed>